  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  showHeroCta={false}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Plans"
  ctaButtonHref="/compare/"
>
  <h2 id="top-picks">Top Picks for Mental Health Coverage</h2>
  <p>
    After evaluating how international health insurers handle mental health, here are our recommendations:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🧠</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Mental Health Coverage</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Strong outpatient therapy coverage, good psychiatry benefits, telehealth options for remote access to care.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💬</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best for Therapy Access</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Allianz Care</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Good network of mental health providers, especially in Europe. Covers therapy and counseling services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🏥</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best for Serious Conditions</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Bupa Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Strong inpatient mental health coverage, good for those who may need intensive treatment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💰</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Budget Option</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">IMG Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">More affordable with mental health included, though with lower limits than premium options.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="why-it-matters">Why Mental Health Coverage Matters Abroad</h2>
  <p>
    Expat life creates unique mental health challenges:
  </p>

  <h3>Culture Shock and Adjustment</h3>
  <p>
    Moving abroad means losing your support network, navigating unfamiliar systems, and adapting to new cultures. This adjustment period causes stress, anxiety, and sometimes depression—even for people without prior mental health issues.
  </p>

  <h3>Isolation and Loneliness</h3>
  <p>
    Remote workers and digital nomads often lack regular social connection. Building friendships abroad takes time. The isolation can significantly impact mental health.
  </p>

  <h3>Career and Financial Stress</h3>
  <p>
    Freelancers and entrepreneurs face income uncertainty. Career transitions abroad add stress. Financial pressure affects mental wellbeing.
  </p>

  <h3>Relationship Strain</h3>
  <p>
    Couples abroad face unique pressures. Long-distance relationships with family and friends back home strain connections. Expat life tests relationships.
  </p>

  <h3>Travel Medical Insurance Doesn't Cover Mental Health</h3>
  <p>
    Here's the problem: budget travel medical plans (SafetyWing, World Nomads) typically exclude mental health entirely or only cover acute crisis situations. If mental health matters to you, you need full international health insurance.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Find Coverage That Includes Mental Health"
    description="Compare full health insurance plans with therapy and psychiatry benefits."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Mental Health Coverage Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Coverage Types Explained</h3>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

